        "description":
          "In your Xentral instance, create a Personal Access Token (PAT) via the API token settings (see https://help.xentral.com/hc/en-us/articles/22627542067740). Grant read scopes for sales orders, products, and customers, plus create scope for sales orders if you want to import orders.",
